"{\"uid\": \"bluemountainsgazette.com.au-story-8710784-blaxland-high-celebrates-fox-sisters-olympic-selection\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"It's not often that two ex-students from the same school are selected for the Olympic Games, which is why Blaxland High has celebrated, uniting behind the efforts of paddlers Jess and Noemie Fox.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 106, \"end\": 114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregory_Blaxland\", \"score\": 0.9988838320151813, \"rank\": 0.0011174142742344437, \"text\": \"Blaxland\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregory_Blaxland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gregory_Blaxland\"}, {\"begin\": 184, \"end\": 194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Noemie Fox\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Noemie_Fox\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Loginor signup to continue reading  The sisters are representing Australia in Paris in slalom canoe/kayak,Jess at her fourth Games, Noemie her first.\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 346, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 262, \"end\": 271, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9999325402663544, \"rank\": 4.9365456722436454e-05, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}, {\"begin\": 275, \"end\": 280, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999900224497463, \"rank\": 9.977649699749264e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So the school went all out on Friday, July 26 dressing in their best green and gold, with balloons, str